cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.DC 

This paper discusses the use of Information Centric Networking (ICN) for secure and robust networking in the industrial IoT. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses hazardous gas sensing in industrial environments, which falls under cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
